            "liquid": "<style>\n  .sk-reviews-wrapper {\n    max-width: 420px;\n    margin: 12px auto;\n    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, sans-serif;\n  }\n  .sk-reviews-title {\n    font-size: 18px;\n    font-weight: 800;\n    color: #1a1a1a;\n    margin: 0 0 14px 0;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  .sk-ticker-wrapper {\n    overflow: hidden;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f9f9f9 0%, #ffffff 100%);\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    padding: 16px 0;\n    margin-bottom: 14px;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .sk-ticker-wrapper::before,\n  .sk-ticker-wrapper::after {\n    content: '';\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 0; bottom: 0;\n    width: 40px;\n    z-index: 2;\n    pointer-events: none;\n  }\n  .sk-ticker-wrapper::before {\n    left: 0;\n    background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(249,249,249,1), rgba(249,249,249,0));\n  }\n  .sk-ticker-wrapper::after {\n    right: 0;\n    background: linear-gradient(to left, rgba(249,249,249,1), rgba(249,249,249,0));\n  }\n  .sk-ticker {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 14px;\n    animation: sk-scroll 45s linear infinite;\n    width: max-content;\n  }\n  @keyframes sk-scroll {\n    0% { transform: translateX(0); }\n    100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }\n  }\n  .sk-ticker:hover {\n    animation-play-state: paused;\n  }\n  .sk-review-card {\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    background: white;\n    border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    padding: 12px 16px;\n    min-width: 240px;\n    max-width: 240px;\n    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\n  }\n  .sk-review-stars {\n    color: #FFB800;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    margin-bottom: 7px;\n  }\n  .sk-review-text {\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #1a1a1a;\n    margin: 0 0 7px 0;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  .sk-review-author {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    color: #888;\n    margin: 0;\n    font-style: italic;\n  }\n  .sk-social-proof {\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 12px;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f5, #fafafa);\n    border-radius: 10px;\n  }\n  .sk-social-proof p { margin: 0; }\n  .sk-social-label {\n    font-size: 12px;\n    color: #666;\n    margin-bottom: 4px !important;\n  }\n  .sk-social-count {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-weight: 800;\n    color: #E8B4B8;\n  }\n</style>\n\n{% assign reviews = \"Sophie M.|Ma peau est plus lumineuse dès la 2ème semaine. Pores resserrés et teint uniforme !,Camille D.|Mes amies me demandent ce que j'ai changé. Je recommande à 100% !,Emma B.|Mes cernes ont diminué de moitié en 3 semaines. Peau vraiment transformée.,Marie L.|Effet liftant visible sur l'ovale du visage. Peau ferme et rebondie.,Léa P.|Meilleur investissement beauté de ma vie ! Fini les crèmes hors de prix.,Julie R.|Les 7 LED font vraiment la différence. Résultats impressionnants !,Isabelle T.|À 52 ans je retrouve l'élasticité de mes 40 ans. Mon dermatologue m'a demandé ce que j'utilisais !,Laura G.|Mâchoire plus dessinée et joues plus toniques en moins d'un mois.,Chloé B.|Ridules nettement diminuées. Teint uniforme et lumineux — je me sens rajeunie.,Manon F.|10 minutes par soir et ma peau est transformée. Je l'ai offert à ma sœur !\" | split: \",\" %}\n\n<div class=\"sk-reviews-wrapper\">\n  <h3 class=\"sk-reviews-title\">💬 Ce que disent nos clientes</h3>\n  <div class=\"sk-ticker-wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"sk-ticker\">\n      {% for review in reviews %}\n        {% assign parts = review | split: \"|\" %}\n        <div class=\"sk-review-card\">\n          <div class=\"sk-review-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n          <p class=\"sk-review-text\">\"{{ parts[1] }}\"</p>\n          <p class=\"sk-review-author\">— {{ parts[0] }} ✓</p>\n        </div>\n      {% endfor %}\n      {% for review in reviews %}\n        {% assign parts = review | split: \"|\" %}\n        <div class=\"sk-review-card\">\n          <div class=\"sk-review-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n          <p class=\"sk-review-text\">\"{{ parts[1] }}\"</p>\n          <p class=\"sk-review-author\">— {{ parts[0] }} ✓</p>\n        </div>\n      {% endfor %}\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"sk-social-proof\">\n    <p class=\"sk-social-label\">Rejoignez des milliers de clientes satisfaites</p>\n    <p class=\"sk-social-count\">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 4.8/5 — 1500+ avis vérifiés</p>\n  </div>\n</div>"
          }
